      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 35,
      "message": "This section should be part of sdnc-image and not overwritten by helm deployment.\n--> Part of CCSDK-3503\nall required variables should be passed by env variables.\nVES_COLLECTOR_ENABLED=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_ENABLED}\nVES_COLLECTOR_TLS_ENABLED=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_TLS_ENABLED}\nVES_COLLECTOR_TRUST_ALL_CERTS=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_TRUST_ALL_CERTS}\nVES_COLLECTOR_USERNAME=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_USERNAME}\nVES_COLLECTOR_PASSWORD=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_PASSWORD}\nVES_COLLECTOR_IP=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_IP}\nVES_COLLECTOR_PORT=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_PORT}\nVES_COLLECTOR_VERSION=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_VERSION} # default v7\nREPORTING_ENTITY_NAME=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_REPORTING_ENTITY_NAME} # default ONAP SDN-R\nEVENTLOG_MSG_DETAIL=${SDNR_VES_COLLECTOR_EVENTLOG_MSG_DETAIL} # default SHORT",
